            <p class= "small-text"> 
              A real-time web application that determines the most frequently used hashtags in Twitter and displaying them on a map in real-time. This project started off as part of my final capstone project <%= link_to "Tweet Sentiment VS Weather", "#sentimentVSweather" %> in attempt to build an application to detect events using twitter feeds.
